  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus comments on the value of his wife's letters and informs her that he has arrived in
     Hilton Head, South Carolina.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1864-11-28">November the 28th 1864</date>
      <name type="place">hilton head south <orig reg="Carolina">Carlina</orig></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute><orig reg="My">Miy</orig> Dear Wife</salute>
    </opener>

    <p> i <orig reg="take">tak</orig>
     <orig reg="my">mi</orig> pen in hand to inform you that i am Well at present and i hope <orig
      reg="When">Whean</orig>
     <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fru</orig> lines reach you <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="may">ma</orig> find you Well and i hope that you <unclear>inJoys</unclear>
     <orig reg="yourself">yor Celf</orig> Well on <orig reg="your">yor</orig> visit and i
      <unclear>lad</unclear>
     <orig reg="three">thee</orig> Days in <unclear>gork</unclear>
     <orig reg="before">be for</orig> i got <orig reg="off">of</orig> and all the
     <unclear>firdes</unclear> i <orig reg="have">heave</orig> got is to hilton head and i <orig
      reg="Can't">Cant</orig> tell <orig reg="When">Whean</orig> i Will get to the <orig
      reg="regiment">redgment</orig> and <orig reg="there">thear</orig> is <orig reg="no">now</orig>
     <orig reg="boats">boates</orig> going <orig reg="away">a way</orig>
     <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <orig reg="some">som</orig>
     <orig reg="time">tim</orig> but i <orig reg="Just">Jest</orig> got <orig reg="here">hear</orig>
     <orig reg="today">to Day</orig> and i <orig reg="thought">thot</orig> i <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="write">rit</orig> and let you <orig reg="know">now</orig> that i got out safe and i
     feel <orig reg="very">verry</orig> Well <orig reg="only">onely</orig> it is <orig reg="very"
      >verry</orig> hot <orig reg="here">hear</orig> but i hope that you Will <orig reg="excuse"
